name: Zulnoon Oshallah
text:
Real Name: Zulnoon Oshallah
Metaverse Name: The Nubetean

Born in 1990 in the Nile valley of the Nuba region in Southern Egypt.

Member of the powerful Halayeb bedouin tribe.

Ring leader of the infamous hacker group "Mawali".

Guardian of the Temple of Nubet ("city of gold") in the Mega-City metaverse.
